Kate's sister Sonia told the Macleay Argus 'this was their last chance' at having children.

'Believe me, they have tried everything and this was not an easy option to take.

'We just want them home with their girls to be with their family.

'Their families have only seen a picture of the little girls and all we want to do is hold them in our arms. It's heartbreaking.'

The couple reportedly missed their planned flight home this week as the Thai authorities blocked them from leaving with their girls.

